<h2 id="synchrony-is-misapplied">Synchrony is Misapplied</h2>

<p>Synchrony is the bane of our existence.</p>

<p>Most of our current programming languages (Rust, Haskell, Python, JS, C, â€¦) have implicit synchrony.</p>

